Content: Have you EVER claimed to be a U.S. citizen (in writing or any other way)?
Translation: 你是否曾聲稱自己是美國公民（以書面或任何其他方式）？

Content: Have you EVER registered to vote or voted in any Federal, state, or local election in the United States?
Translation: 你是否曾在美國的任何聯邦、州或地方選舉中登記投票或參與投票？

Content: Do you currently owe any overdue Federal, state, or local taxes in the United States?
Translation: 你目前是否在美國欠任何過期的聯邦、州或地方稅款？

Content: Since you became a lawful permanent resident, have you ever called yourself a 'nonresident alien' on a Federal, state, or local tax return?
Translation: 自從你成為合法永久居民後，你是否曾在聯邦、州或地方納稅申報表上稱自己為「非居民外僑」？

Content: Have you EVER Been a member of any Communist or totalitarian party?
Translation: 你是否曾是任何共產黨或極權政黨的成員？

Content: Have you EVER Advocated the overthrow of the Government by force?
Translation: 你是否曾擁護以武力推翻政府？

Content: Have you EVER provided money or support to a group that used weapons or explosives?
Translation: 你是否曾向使用武器或爆炸物的組織提供金錢或支持？

Content: Have you EVER participated in genocide or killing any person?
Translation: 你是否曾參與過種族滅絕或殺害任何人？

Content: Have you EVER served in any military or police unit?
Translation: 你是否曾服役於任何軍隊或警察部隊？

Content: Have you EVER served in any armed group, rebel group, or guerrilla group?
Translation: 你是否曾服役於任何武裝團體、反叛組織或游擊隊？

Content: Have you EVER worked in a prison, jail, or detention facility?
Translation: 你是否曾在監獄、看守所或拘留所工作過？

Content: Were you EVER a part of any group that used a weapon against any person?
Translation: 你是否曾是任何對他人使用武器的團體的一員？

Content: Have you EVER sold, provided, or transported weapons?
Translation: 你是否曾出售、提供或運輸過武器？

Content: Have you EVER received any weapons training or military training?
Translation: 你是否曾接受過任何武器訓練或軍事訓練？

Content: Have you EVER used any person under 15 years of age to serve in an armed group?
Translation: 你是否曾利用過任何未滿 15 歲的人加入武裝團體？

Content: Have you EVER used any person under 15 years of age to take part in hostilities?
Translation: 你是否曾利用過任何未滿 15 歲的人參加敵對行動？

Content: Have you EVER committed a crime for which you were NOT arrested?
Translation: 你是否曾犯下任何你「沒有」被逮捕的罪行？

Content: Have you EVER been arrested, cited, or detained by any law enforcement officer?
Translation: 你是否曾被任何執法官員逮捕、傳喚或拘留？

Content: If you received a suspended sentence or probation, have you completed it?
Translation: 如果你被判處緩刑，你是否已經完成？

Content: Have you EVER Engaged in prostitution?
Have you EVER sold or smuggled illegal drugs or narcotics?
Translation: 你是否曾銷售或走私非法藥物或麻醉品？

Content: Have you EVER Been married to more than one person at the same time?
Translation: 你是否曾同時與超過一人結婚？

Content: Have you EVER Married someone in order to obtain an immigration benefit?
Translation: 你是否曾為了獲得移民利益而與某人結婚？

Content: Have you EVER Helped anyone to enter the United States illegally?
Translation: 你是否曾協助任何人非法進入美國？

Content: Have you EVER Gambled illegally?
Have you EVER Failed to support your dependents or to pay alimony?
Translation: 你是否曾未能撫養你的受撫養人或支付贍養費？

Content: Have you EVER Made any misrepresentation to obtain any public benefit?
Translation: 你是否曾為了獲得任何公共福利而做出任何虛假陳述？

Content: Have you EVER given any U.S. Government officials any false information?
Translation: 你是否曾向任何美國政府官員提供過虛假資訊？

Content: Have you EVER lied to any U.S. Government officials to gain entry into the U.S.?
Translation: 你是否曾向任何美國政府官員撒謊以便進入美國？

Content: Have you EVER been placed in removal or deportation proceedings?
Translation: 你是否曾被列入驅逐或遣返程序？

Content: Have you EVER been removed or deported from the United States?
Translation: 你是否曾被從美國移送或驅逐出境？

Content: Have you EVER left the United States to avoid being drafted?
Translation: 你是否曾為了逃避徵兵而離開美國？

Content: Have you EVER applied for any kind of exemption from military service?
Translation: 你是否曾申請過免除服兵役的任何豁免？

Content: Have you EVER served in the U.S. armed forces?
Translation: 你是否曾在美國武裝部隊服役？

Content: Are you currently a member of the U.S. armed forces?
Translation: 你目前是美國武裝部隊的成員嗎？

Content: Are you a former U.S. military service member residing outside the U.S.?
Translation: 你是否是居住在境外的美國退役軍人？

Content: Have you EVER been court-martialed while in the U.S. armed forces?
Translation: 在美國武裝部隊期間，你是否曾受過軍事法庭審判？

Content: Have you EVER been discharged from service because you were an alien?
Translation: 你是否曾因為是外籍人士而退役？

Content: Have you EVER deserted from the U.S. armed forces?
Translation: 你是否曾在美國武裝部隊中逃兵？

Content: Do you now have a hereditary title or nobility in any foreign country?
Translation: 你現在在任何外國擁有世襲頭銜或貴族爵位嗎？

Content: Do you support the Constitution and form of Government of the United States?
Translation: 你是否支持美國憲法和美國政府形式？

Content: Do you understand the full Oath of Allegiance to the United States?
Translation: 你是否理解對美國完整的效忠誓言？

Content: Are you unable to take the Oath of Allegiance because of a disability?
Translation: 你是否因為殘疾而無法進行效忠宣誓？

Content: Are you willing to take the full Oath of Allegiance to the United States?
Translation: 你是否願意宣讀對美國完整的效忠誓言？

Content: If the law requires it, are you willing to bear arms on behalf of the United States?
Translation: 如果法律要求，你是否願意代表美國拿起武器？

Content: If the law requires it, are you willing to perform noncombatant services?
Translation: 如果法律要求，你是否願意從事非戰鬥服務？

Content: If the law requires it, are you willing to perform work of national importance?
Translation: 如果法律要求，你是否願意從事對國家有重大影響的工作？
